{"id":171493,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011810/","date":"2011-08-11T01:00:36Z","modified":"2011-09-27T17:08:26Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/8/10","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【美国国债降级</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">】</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.reuters.com/great-debate/2011/08/08/can-china-afford-to-downgrade-the-u-s/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国能承受得了美国国债降级吗？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——认为中国威胁卖出美国国债就可令美国屈服的人，只看到了问题的一个方面</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金融时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.ft.com/beyond-brics/2011/08/08/china-and-us-debt-a-sanctimonious-drug-dealer/#axzz1UQNcuzYu\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在美国国债问题上，中国就像正言厉色的毒品贩子</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——对于华盛顿的财政危机，北京至少也负有部分责任</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2011/aug/08/china-criticism-usa-industrialisation-slow\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国批评美国的背后，是对自身工业化速度减缓的担忧</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《中国日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/bizchina/2011-08/10/content_13087089.htm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大公国际给予铁道部</span>3A<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">级评级</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——比中国本外币</span></span><span><span>2A+</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">评级还高那么一点</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">点</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">社</span>：</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110810/ap_on_re_as/as_china_human_rights\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大胆直言的博主冉云飞在被关押</span>6<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个月之后获释</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/10/world/asia/10artist.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">异议艺术家艾未未打破沉默，发推批评中国政</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">府</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.globaltimes.cn/NEWS/tabid/99/articleType/ArticleView/articleId/670150/Exclusive-Ai-Weiwei-breaks-his-silence.aspx\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艾未未独家采访</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这真是一家精神分裂的报纸。能有这样的英文采访，也能有以前的中文社论</span></span><span><span>…</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">经济观察：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economonitor.com/analysts/2011/08/09/how-will-the-rise-of-china%E2%80%99s-new-regional-economic-centers-affect-the-2012-political-transition/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国新的地区经济中心将如何影响</span>2012<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">政治交接？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——重庆、天津、福建等地的经济发展，对</span></span><span><span>2012</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的交接带来变化</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国听说博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinahearsay.com/china-net-rumors-and-food-safety-speech-versus-commerce/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国网络流言与食品安全：言论与商业</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“从长期看，谣言并不是问题，公众对谣言的重视才是更大的问题”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国立场博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://sinostand.com/2011/08/07/how-to-write-a-chinese-editorial/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">从《环球时报》看如何写中文社论？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span> 1</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）把问题变成“中、西方”对立；</span></span><span><span>2</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）先立假靶子，再打倒之；</span></span><span><span>3</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span></span><span><span>…</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交关系委员会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cfr.org/china/chinas-growing-water-crisis/p25617?cid=rss-asia-china_s_growing_water_crisis-080911&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+region%2Fasia+%28CFR.org+-+Regions+-+Asia%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国日趋严重的水危机</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“在中国几千年历史上，人与自然之间的冲突从没象现在这样严重”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/8691706/Pork-price-rises-drive-up-Chinese-inflation.htmlhttp:/www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/8691706/Pork-price-rises-drive-up-Chinese-inflation.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国通胀指数上月达到</span>6.5%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，都是猪肉惹得</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">祸</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110810/ts_nm/us_china_usa_fed\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国官员称，物价已经到顶，但风险仍存</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，包括可能的美国新一轮量化宽</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">松</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111904480904576497962651886944.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国推动其巨量的安居房建设</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——发展经济同时维护社会稳定；然而人们担忧资金短缺，建设质量堪</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">忧</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/09/china-debt-idUSL3E7J92VO20110809\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">温家宝呼吁全球合作，稳定市场</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——敦促各国采取负责任的金融政策，减少赤字；在谈到中国抑制通货膨胀时语气变得温</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/10/china-aircraft-carrier-launch\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在地区局势紧张之时，中国第一艘航母下</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">水</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/aug/09/conocophillips-oil-spill-china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">康菲石油清理中国渤海湾原油泄露动作缓慢</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/10/world/asia/10briefs-cyberattacks.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国称，</span>2010<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年受到</span>50<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万次网络攻击</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>15%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">来自美</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111904480904576497983432884002.html?mod=googlenews_wsj\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">民进党称成为中国黑客潮的目标</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——电脑每日被入侵，影响其准备明年</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月的总统大</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">选</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业内幕》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/four-reasons-why-china-will-dominate-eurasia-2011-8?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+businessinsider+%28Business+Insider%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国将统治欧亚的四个原因</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——人口膨胀、资源紧张、女性短缺、霸权历史</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalpublicsquare.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/09/what-will-vice-president-biden-find-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">拜登访问中国会发现什么？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国崛起依赖经济增长，然而增长不可持</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">续</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福克斯新闻》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2011/08/09/critics-question-us-aid-to-china-amid-debt-woes/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">随着美债危机</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">加剧</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，批评</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">家质疑美国对华</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外援计划</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福克斯新闻》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2011/08/09/us-shells-out-aid-for-africa-as-china-russia-hold-back/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国出钱援助非洲，中俄袖手旁观</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管深陷债务，美国增加对非洲干旱援助；中俄笑话美国处理债务不当，却出手吝</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">啬</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2011/aug/09/london-riots-iran\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">各国对伦敦骚乱幸灾乐祸，伊朗拔得头</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">筹</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/police-use-water-canons-batons-to-control-angry-protest-in-indian-capital-against-corruption/article2124177/?utm_medium=Feeds:%20RSS/Atom\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">警察采用竹警棍水龙控制反腐游</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">行</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/meast/08/09/us.syria/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国准备直接要求阿萨德下</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/10/north-south-korea-defence-minister-plot\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">媒体报道，北朝鲜派遣特务暗杀韩国防</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">长</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/blogs/banyan/2011/08/north-korean-computer-hackers?fsrc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">赏金黑客</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——北朝鲜的计算机高手受雇盗取南朝鲜网络游戏公司的大量资金</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/08/09/the-danger-to-china%E2%80%99s-economy/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国经济面临的危险</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——不管是继续投资拉动经济，还是致力建设中产阶级，中国政府不可能永远不受自然规律约束</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-09/china-may-delay-rate-rises-until-2012-on-financial-chaos-.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国可能会将加息推迟到</span>2012<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国领导人呼吁全球合作稳定金融市场之后，中国可能将步韩印等国后尘延迟加</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">息</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111904140604576499290300628416.html?mod=googlenews_wsj\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国宣布两年半以来最大顺差，人民币汇率冲到新高</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——坊间猜测中国可能会允许人民币升值，以抑制通货膨</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">胀</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/10/business/global/chinese-trade-surplus-rises-sharply.html?partner=rssnyt\">7<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月份，中国进出口增长均高于预期</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——贸易顺差达到两年半来最高水平，</span></span><span><span>315</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">元</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/09/us-china-cdm-point-carbon-idUSTRE7783PE20110809\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国打算设立工业</span>CO2<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">排放限额</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，然而此举并不足以说服欧盟按照清洁发展机制继续为中国清洁项目付</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">费</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-10/korea-bans-short-selling-as-state-run-funds-signal-buying.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">自今日起到</span>11<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span>9<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日，韩国禁止股票短线卖出</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；政府力图支持救市，两个最大的国有基金称将加大投</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">资</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-09/singapore-cuts-export-growth-forecast-as-global-risks-rise.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">随着美欧经济不振债务危机蔓延，新加坡调低今年出口增长预</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">期</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/10/world/asia/10mistress.html?partner=rssnyt\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国新富创造二奶市</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">场</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/10/chinese-social-insurance-will-foreigners-be-able-to-opt-out/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国新法规定在华工作外国人需加入中国社保系</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">统</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/8691111/Explorer-Marco-Polo-never-actually-went-to-China.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">马可波罗从未到过中国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他的中国游记使他成为最著名的旅行家之一，但现在考古学家们认为他从未到过那里</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>MSNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" h